{"word":"ἐϋκτίμενος","slug":"ἐϋκτίμενος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n44338\" key=\"e)u+kti/menos\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἐϋκτίμενος</orth> [<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ῐ], <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">η</itype>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>, (kti/zw)</foreign> <sense id=\"n44338.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">εὖ ναιόμενος</ref></xr>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">good to dwell in</tr_>, epith. of cities, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐϋ. πτολίεθρον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:501\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.501</biblScope></bibl></cit>, etc.; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πόλις</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0199.tlg001:5:149\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ B.\">B.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.149</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; of anything on which man's labour has been bestowed, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">νῆσον ἐϋκτιμένην ἐκάμοντο</foreign> wrought it <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">so as to be good to dwell in</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:9:130\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.130</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐϋ. ἐν ἀλωῇ</foreign> on a <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">well-made</tr_> threshing-floor, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:20:496\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">20.496</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:21:77\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.77</biblScope> </bibl>; the same phrase, of a garden, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">well-wrought</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:24:226\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">24.226</biblScope></bibl>. (<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">εὐκτ</foreign>- in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0013.tlg003.perseus-grc1:36\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ h.Ap.\">h.Ap.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">36</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ B.\">B.</a></author> </bibl> l.c.)</sense> </entryFree>"}]}